reviews.review_text:
Sounds terrific Another terrific sounding AUD from Mr. Rolfe and Mr. Minches.  Keep up the great work gents!

Show is pretty good - Jerry flubs shakedown vocals, but what's a GD show without vocal flubs anyway?

Rating is for the quality of the recording/transfer.

Intense Shows 
You had to be there 
Jerry was very wasted,  yellow beard and fingers
Dandruff and food all over his shirt 
Legs swollen 
Band was very angry at him 
Show was one of the greatest ever
